      <section id="details">
        <h2 class="gem-c-heading gem-c-heading--font-size-27 gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  ">Details</h2>


        
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
    
          <div class="govspeak">
<p>CC News is emailed to all charity contacts, with instruction to forward to their trustees. It contains essential regulatory information that charities need to be aware of.</p>

<p>This issue includes articles about:</p>

<ul>
  <li>new user-friendly guides for charity trustees</li>
  <li>coronavirus (COVID-19) guidance for charities</li>
  <li>our Annual Public Meeting</li>
  <li>charity fraud awareness</li>
  <li>new register of charities</li>
  <li>the UK and EU transition</li>
  <li>how to get help to revitalise your charity funds</li>
  <li>keeping in touch with us</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="app-c-published-dates " lang="en">
    Published 5 November 2020
